snippet.title: Sky Fleet Trailer
snippet.description:
SKY FLEET on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1347540/Sky_Fleet/

SKY FLEET is a co-op shooter, tower defense and base building game about defending your floating islands. Drones have invaded and are mining your islands draining them of life. Build a city above the clouds and gather resources so that you can fight them back.
